How to modify my company`s information?

Changing your company's information at mobilize events will allow your clients
to feel "at home" when organizing their Event in your environment.

Keeping your information up to date will also be good for us to advertise your
Company on our communication channels!

Editing the Company's information

To access the Access Permissions, on the top right corner click on Settings >
My Company.

You'll see a screen like this one:
[image]

After updating your information and inserting a logo, click on the Save button.
